stimulus:
A rating scale as shown below is used throughout the task. You will select any point with your mouse.
Choose any point on the scale and click 'Submit' to continue.
During the task, if you are very sure that you made the correct judgement, you should respond 'Certain'
If you are very unsure you made the correct judgement, you should respond 'Guessing'
If you are somewhat sure about being correct, you should select a rating between the two descriptions.
If you understand how to use and take advantage of the whole rating scale, choose any point on the rating scale and click 'Submit' to continue.
